snippet.title: EverQuest: The Burning Lands Expansion Stream
snippet.description:
Catch the replay of the EverQuest: The Burning Lands expansion livestream with the team for a first look at the game's 25th expansion!

The Burning Lands is available for pre-order now at https://www.everquest.com/expansion-content

This stream was recorded live and broadcast on https://www.facebook.com/EverQuestLive/ on Tuesday, October 30, 2018 at 10AM PT!

Play EQ for free: https://www.everquest.com/register
